{"id":"5e9c302a9b6559241525daf3","artists":["5e9b694b7a1236eccfeb2594"],"title":"New: Sun Glitters – The Wind Caresses Her Hair","content":"<p><a rel=\"attachment wp-att-8951\" href=\"https://admin.</p><p>crackintheroad.com/music/new-sun-glitters-the-wind-caresses-her-hair/attachment/sunwind/\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-8951\" title=\"sunwind\" src=\"https://api.crackintheroad.com/uploads/2011/07/sunwind.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://api.crackintheroad.com/images/2011/07/sunwind.jpg 600w, https://api.crackintheroad.com/images/2011/07/sunwind-165x165.jpg 165w, https://api.crackintheroad.com/images/2011/07/sunwind-260x260.jpg 260w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>Sun Glitters’</strong> new track ‘<em>the wind caresses her hair</em>’ is exactly what you’d expect from the man who has remarkably suddenly, changed the landscape of underground beat music. The track hinges around a repeated human voice sample, a muted reverse looped sound, which although seemingly meaningless, manages to encompass a human of loneliness. Elsewhere, the sounds are dissonant and consuming, the beats are eerily disinterested in the piece and the synths are as perfectly layered and richly textured as ever. A great track.</p>\n<p><iframe width=\"400\" height=\"100\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; width: 400px; height: 100px;\" src=\"https://bandcamp.com/EmbeddedPlayer/v=2/track=92547966/size=venti/bgcol=FFFFFF/linkcol=4285BB/\" allowtransparency=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\"><a href=\"https://sunglitters.bandcamp.com/track/the-wind-caresses-her-hair\">the wind caresses her hair by Sun Glitters</a></iframe></p>\n","slug":"8950-new-sun-glitters-the-wind-caresses-her-hair","category":"music","date":1309525254000,"wpid":8950,"isSticky":false,"featured_image":{"width":165,"height":165,"src":"2011/07/sunwind-165x165.jpg","placeholder":"data:image/jpeg;base64, "},"createdAt":1587294250142,"updatedAt":15884035534